text: Pisanella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Species== Species within the genus Pisanella include: * Pisanella antiquata (Hinds, 1844): synonym of Tritonoharpa antiquata ==References== * Hemmen J. title: Pisanella
